    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >人类的命运失败了。在比邻星B上发现的PBB-1细菌向人类展示，他们并不像曾经相信的那样掌控宇宙。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >与感染者战斗，争取生存</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PBB-1与有机物质结合，传播并吞噬一切。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197230/extras/51795c5ccad7c9b4675a7fc3c5ee6867.poster.avif?t=1737988248\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197230/extras/51795c5ccad7c9b4675a7fc3c5ee6867.webm?t=1737988248\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197230/extras/51795c5ccad7c9b4675a7fc3c5ee6867.mp4?t=1737988248\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在太空中漂浮时，补给有限</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集资源，但要明智地使用它们。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197230/extras/6eccbc3b6252e831d34004d57817902a.poster.avif?t=1737988248\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197230/extras/6eccbc3b6252e831d34004d57817902a.webm?t=1737988248\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197230/extras/6eccbc3b6252e831d34004d57817902a.mp4?t=1737988248\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >悄悄绕过感染者，避免浪费珍贵的弹药</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择不战斗始终是一个选择。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197230/extras/2c74cc297e3e01625c5a0328e0b99b1f.poster.avif?t=1737988248\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197230/extras/2c74cc297e3e01625c5a0328e0b99b1f.webm?t=1737988248\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197230/extras/2c74cc297e3e01625c5a0328e0b99b1f.mp4?t=1737988248\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索SS Destiny的3个楼层</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3个楼层提供不同的环境、视觉、补给和战斗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197230/extras/5c945733f1da09311905c502d95c8498.poster.avif?t=1737988248\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197230/extras/5c945733f1da09311905c502d95c8498.webm?t=1737988248\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197230/extras/5c945733f1da09311905c502d95c8498.mp4?t=1737988248\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
